ERN-LUNG (European Reference Network on Rare Pulmonary Diseases) covers a wide range of rare lung diseases and features a sub-group on interstitial lung diseases that also includes IPF. EU-IPFF works together with ERN-LUNG as an ePAG: an elected patient representatives who will ensure that the patient voice is heard throughout the ERN development process.&#xd;
&#xd;
Liam Galvin, the EU-IPFF Secretary, is also a member of the ELF Patient Advisory Committee.
